Text.string: Are your friends like, “Slow down, speedy, I'm eating a hoagie here?”||Do you have a positive association with the word “skidmarks”?||Then it's time to drive! Name's Prisa. Hop into that outrunner and let's ride!
We've got ourselves a driver! If you can prove you're the sultan of stunts, you'll become the official driver of Grog Lube! “Grog Lube: get quick, slick!”
Guts for days! Grog Lube is gonna be all over you, slick! Now, you ready for THE BIG JUMP?! It's a three-parter, and my daddy was the only driver I ever saw make this one.
Slick. You serious?
Ouch. Gonna pretend I didn't see that.
You fall asleep or somethin'?
Not even close. Come on, slick! Flog that Grog!
Guess you're not Grog Lube material! Prove me wrong!
You made it! My daddy would've loved to see that! He was the official stunt driver of Grog Lube... until the big crash. That's his old ride.
He ran outta Grog Lube. The engine cut out, left him stranded. COV got him—but I could never make the jump myself. You mind destroyin' his car? Don't want any bandits taking it.
Thanks. Wish my daddy were around to see you drive. Help yourself to his stash. It's all yours, slick.
Grog Lube: it takes guts. And you got guts for days, slick. I think it's safe to say you're Grog Lube material!
Head on back to the garage. Fresh outrunner waiting for ya.
You sure you're all right to drive, slick? Got another outrunner at the garage for ya.
I'm not sure you're Grog Lube material, slick. But head to the garage and give it another try.
Destroyed another outrunner, huh? Well... you know where to go.
The speed demon has arrived! Hit these ramps to prove you're ready for the BIG TIME!
Get in the car, slick.
You can't prove you're Grog Lube material if you're not drivin'!
Why'd you get out of your car? You're not scared, are ya?
Your car misses you, slick. Don't you wanna drive fast?
If you junk my outrunner, just swing by the garage. I've got a few spares.
Not bad. You just might be Grog Lube sponsorship material, slick!
Killer. You're oozing Grog Lube style!
Give those pistons a mistin' with Grog Lube!
Grog Lube: drivin' good takes guts.
One more test, and then it's time for the BIG ONE!
Flog that grog and boost!
You afraid of the boost? EMBRACE THE BOOST!
Hit the boost, slick! The boost!
Weak jump. Maybe you should just go home, slick.
Get loose and hit the JUICE!
